Class PlanTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.single.cypher.planning.plantable.PlanTable

    Iterable<PlanTableEntry>

    public class PlanTable
extends Object
implements Iterable<PlanTableEntry>
    A data structure to manage multiple query plans. Each QueryPlan is represented by a PlanTableEntry.
